title: Damkutla Dumkutla Lyrics TNPL Anthem
stanzas:
Damkutla Dumkutla
udukutla adungutla
thenna matta
paricha atta
engalukku bat-tu

Damkutla Dumkutla
udukutla adungutla
sevura stump-a
mathiduvom
moonu koda pottu

naanga nara nara
enga adi thara thara
edhuku vara vara
yaaru ingae
ara kora.

Damkutla Dumkutla
udukutla adungutla
thenna matta
paricha atta
engalukku bat-tu

Damkutla Dumkutla
udukutla adungutla
sevura stump-a
mathiduvom
moonu koda pottu

moodiginnu konjam othu
semma matter thaan
namma TNPL maappu
